title: AmTrust Financial Services (AFSI) Stock is the 'Chart of the Day'
text:
AmTrust Financial Services ( AFSI down by 0.60% to $66.06 in afternoon trading on Tuesday.
The New York City-based insurance holding company hit a 52-week high late last month as shares rose to $63.30 on June 19.
Insight From TheStreet Research Team:
AmTrust Financial Services is the subject of today's 'Chart of the Day ' analysis by Trifecta Stocks ' Bryan Ashenberg and Bob Lang. Here is what they had to say about the company:
AmTrust Financial Services is one of those rare financial names that continues to make higher highs and higher lows.
Relative strength has been impressive for months, and volume trends continue to build.
The momentum indicators at the bottom are on buy signals, and we see there have been opportunities to get on board.
This would be a good add at the lower end of the channel.
- Bryan Ashenberg and Bob Lang , ' Chart of the Day: AFSI ', originally published 7/14/15 on TrifectaStocks.com
